description:
Joyce Maynard is seduced by an inmate with extraordinary letter-writiing skills. &nbsp;
Kemp Powers is only 14 when he learns that playing with a loaded gun can have devastating consequences. &nbsp;
A. E. Hotchner lets Ernest Hemmingway talk him into dressing like a matador to face a bull in Spain.
 Hosted by The Moth's Aristic Director, Catherine Burns.
